Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow of the LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor system:

```plantuml
@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor

participant "Waze CCP Data Feed" as WazeFeed
participant "waze-data-download\nLambda" as DownloadLambda
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS
participant "waze-data-process\nLambda" as ProcessLambda
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "Specialized Processing\nLambdas" as SpecializedLambdas
participant "Aurora PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "waze-data-api\nLambda" as APILambda
participant "Client" as Client

activate DownloadLambda
DownloadLambda -> WazeFeed: Fetch data
WazeFeed --> DownloadLambda: Return data
DownloadLambda -> S3: Store JSON files
DownloadLambda -> SNS: Notify data retrieval
deactivate DownloadLambda

S3 -> ProcessLambda: Trigger event
activate ProcessLambda
ProcessLambda -> S3: Retrieve JSON files
ProcessLambda -> SQS: Enqueue processing tasks
deactivate ProcessLambda

SQS -> SpecializedLambdas: Trigger processing
activate SpecializedLambdas
SpecializedLambdas -> DB: Store processed data
SpecializedLambdas --> SQS: Processing complete
deactivate SpecializedLambdas

Client -> APIGateway: Request data
activate APIGateway
APIGateway -> APILambda: Forward request
activate APILambda
APILambda -> DB: Query data
DB --> APILambda: Return data
APILambda --> APIGateway: Return response
deactivate APILambda
APIGateway --> Client: Deliver response
deactivate APIGateway

@enduml
```